Modified `render_diff` to display the subtask description between the status bar (row 1) and the diff area. Added a `wrap_text` helper that word-wraps text to a given width. Description lines render in dimmed style (`\x1b[2m`) starting at row 2, followed by a horizontal rule separator (`─` repeated). The diff area's starting row and `visible_rows` calculation now account for the description block height (description lines + separator), so scrolling remains correct.